plyTime":"2019-04-02T02:33:06.000Z","msg":"閪媒用google translate?<br />\n日本內閣官房長官同安倍，都解釋咗出處同意思啦，依家傳媒真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"d661767044fc718ed295a57ff41bfc97716afa1d","tid":1087974,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:37:43.000Z","msg":"Love and peace"},{"pid":"81a0d5c7f59d0a93a3473aa657f1109a272775de","tid":1087974,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d3e958962917ee826f891fa476e2fa7f9bc8ed3","tid":1087974,"uid":35315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:16:11.000Z","msg":"有濃厚文化根基又民族主義強嘅社會真係令人羨慕"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:38:13.000Z","msg":"除左家臣主義同老婆奴之外其他幾好"},{"pid":"d0db893f0cd4460accf98a62fecbfc2fd21adfd4","tid":1087974,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81a0d5c7f59d0a93a3473aa657f1109a272775de","tid":1087974,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d3e958962917ee826f891fa476e2fa7f9bc8ed3","tid":1087974,"uid":35315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:16:11.000Z","msg":"有濃厚文化根基又民族主義強嘅社會真係令人羨慕"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:38:13.000Z","msg":"除左家臣主義同老婆奴之外其他幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:38:53.000Z","msg":"其優遠勝其壞"},{"pid":"013badccd269c5b5ac344d8dd7702f5a5e63ee3c","tid":1087974,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"cb2e33b531313415293e355417054c6529e14786","tid":1087974,"uid":131245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ac7e4327b9033c26c3d26a0297adc49fb8b52060","tid":1087974,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T16:46:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/12944/3731497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F12944%2F3731497&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQi0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=93c3e454\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/12944/3731497</a><br />\n日本德仁皇太子將於5月1日登基，為平成時代劃上句號。內閣官房長官菅義偉周一（4月1日）宣布新年號為「令和」，但到底英語圈傳媒如何為這個新年號解畫？<br />\n「令和」的英文拼音為「Reiwa」，「和」字在日本有「和平」、「和諧」之義，在日本年號史上屬「常客」，因此英語媒體將之譯為「peace」或「harmony」實屬正常之舉。<br />\n<br />\n由於這次是日本年號首次採用「令」字，所以在翻譯時顯得有難度。彭博社（Bloomberg）、英國廣播公司（BBC）都是以「Order」（秩序）解釋「令」字的意思，《衛報》（Guardian）則以「decree」（政令）看待，更提到電視台的評論員一時之間找不到合適的翻譯用詞。<br />\n<br />\n日本網民都很關心外國媒體的報道，對於BBC以「order and harmony」形容「令和」字面上的意思，有不少人認為這個譯法很「有型」。<br />\n<br />\n根據日本政府解畫，「令和」的出處是日本古典詩歌總集《萬葉集》的其中一首：「初春令月，氣淑風和」。「令」有「美好」的意思，因此《華爾街日報》以「auspicious」（吉祥）形容，算是較為貼切的譯法。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T00:27:14.000Z","msg":"MK仔女講你好令，即係BEAUTIFUL / GOOD LOOKING / SMART<br />\n<br />\nbeautiful and harmony"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"「令」的確係美好既意思<br />\n標音係「靈」<br />\n<br />\n廣府話變音為「leng3」<br />\n即係俗話既「靚」<br />\n<br />\n（「靚」讀音係「淨）」"},{"pid":"79a9d2d5dbfdf2fd8bdfb3e429f7bb83034d8fa1","tid":1087974,"uid":12421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1346f07051a68afc7cc89ac951dd671df756c12e","tid":1087974,"uid":62506,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:32:04.000Z","msg":"直接用Reiwa算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T03:03:26.000Z","msg":"咁報紙佬都要延伸下閱讀 解釋個字點解㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n似香港啲垃圾照抄就當一篇新聞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259eeebddb56a72b7d124f1d94f8ca5e3b240a81","tid":1087974,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a53a51c4d91434e2dabe915861e4c1c492450ff2","tid":1087974,"uid":109462,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"a4f2797cbc0ee7709063a5ad92a1b0186cbc50ab","tid":1087974,"uid":106864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b54ffd327d5bdffedffc5a0563c2ec0083c65a9a","tid":1087974,"uid":1149,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:02:07.000Z","msg":"咪係，平成又有咩意思 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T23:43:30.000Z","msg":"內平外成，google咗先講野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr